comments: Curry (GSW) releases from the contact with Martin (CHA) before his jump shot attempt.
Wiggins (GSW) places a hand to Ball's (CHA) front during the drive but the contact is marginal and does not affect his SQBR.
The Hornets did not release their shot attempt before the shot clock expired.
Green (GSW) shuffles his feet at the start of his dribble on the perimeter.
Green (GSW) makes marginal contact with Bridges (CHA) in the post that does not affect his shot attempt.
Plumlee (CHA) brings his arm forward and makes contact to Looney's (GSW) arm that affects his shot attempt.
Green (GSW) gets his hand on the ball while defending Rozier (CHA) and any contact is incidental.  A held ball is correctly called.
Looney (GSW) makes contact to Rozier's (CHA) arm that affects his SQBR.
Ball (CHA) maintains a legal guarding position during the play at the basket by Lee (GSW) and the contact is incidental.
